# Keep these IntelliJ config files (shared project settings):
# .idea/compiler.xml      → bytecode target
# .idea/misc.xml          → SDK + language level
# .idea/vcs.xml           → VCS mappings
# .idea/runConfigurations/ → Run configs with JVM args

